```r
```r
N = 1000  #Simulations

PPI = fread(\../data/PPI_Symbol_Entrez.csv\)

gPPI = PPI[, c(3,4)] %>%
  graph_from_data_frame(., directed = F) %>%
  simplify() %>%
  delete.vertices(v=\\)

Genes_nR = fread(\../data/out/CoDINA/CN_nR.txt\, header = F)
Genes_R = fread(\../data/out/CoDINA/CN_R.txt\, header = F)
Genes_RnR = fread(\../data/out/CoDINA/CN_a.txt\, header = F)
###
### add genes known to RA
Genes_RA = fread(\../data/RA_Genes.txt\, header = F)
Genes_RA %<>% filter(V1 %in% V(gPPI)$name)

Genes_nR$type = \non resp\
Genes_R$type = \resp\
Genes_RnR$type = \common\
Genes_RA$type = \RA\

Jac = Jaccard(All[,c(2,1)])

## Calculate the proximity to Scipher selected drugs


<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxuU2NpcGhlckRydWdzID0gcmVhZHhsOjpyZWFkX2V4Y2VsKFxcLi4vZGF0YS9EcnVnU2NpcGhlci54bHN4XFwpXG5cbkRCID0gZnJlYWQoXFwuLi9kYXRhL0RCX0RydWdUYXJnZXRzXzEyMDEuY3N2XFwpXG5cbkRCICU8PiUgXG4gIGZpbHRlcihHZW5lX1RhcmdldCAlaW4lIFYoZ1BQSSkkbmFtZSkgJT4lXG4gIGZpbHRlcihOYW1lICVpbiUgU2NpcGhlckRydWdzJERydWcpICU+JVxuICBzZWxlY3QoTmFtZSwgR2VuZV9UYXJnZXQpICU+JSBcbiAgdW5pcXVlKClcblxuIyBBbW91bnQgb2YgdGFyZ2V0cyBwZXIgZHJ1Z1xuREIgJT4lXG4gIGdyb3VwX2J5KE5hbWUpICU+JVxuICBzdW1tYXJpc2UobiA9IG4oKSkgJT4lXG4gIGFycmFuZ2UoZGVzYyhuKSlcbmBgYFxuYGBgIn0= -->

```r
```r
ScipherDrugs = readxl::read_excel(\../data/DrugScipher.xlsx\)

DB = fread(\../data/DB_DrugTargets_1201.csv\)

DB %<>% 
  filter(Gene_Target %in% V(gPPI)$name) %>%
  filter(Name %in% ScipherDrugs$Drug) %>%
  select(Name, Gene_Target) %>% 
  unique()

# Amount of targets per drug
DB %>%
  group_by(Name) %>%
  summarise(n = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc(n))

```r
# Calculate the proximity
# 
names(DB) = c('ID', "Target" )
proximity_RA = avr_proximity_multiple_target_sets(
  set = unique(DB$ID),
  G = gPPI,
  ST = DB,
  source = Genes_RA$V1,
  N = N
)
proximity_RA

proximity_RA %>% 
  filter(p.adjust(p_lt) < 0.001)
proximity_nR = avr_proximity_multiple_target_sets(
  set = unique(DB$ID),
  G = gPPI,
  ST = DB,
  source = Genes_nR$V1,
  N = N
)
proximity_nR

proximity_nR %>% 
  filter(p.adjust(p_lt) < 0.001)

```r
proximity_nR_RnR = avr_proximity_multiple_target_sets(
  set = unique(DB$ID),
  G = gPPI,
  ST = DB,
  source = c(Genes_nR$V1, Genes_RnR$V1),
  N = N
